{"tid":804407,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"掌摑打頭起腳踢面　八旬台灣老翁被印傭虐待無力反抗","createTime":"2018-09-03T03:52:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T04:18:43.000Z","uid":150685,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b0acfd8ea51294adeebc3d1f0c5b7b04052f35c3","tid":804407,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T03:52:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BRWjjaYAqpE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBRWjjaYAqpE&d=hzNM7YY%2BVeW%2BoBM08pddX0zHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=847f9632\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BRWjjaYAqpE</a><br />\n<br />\n外傭虐待少主時有聽聞。台灣有網民上傳自己80歲爺爺，遭受印尼籍外傭虐待的片段，聲稱拍片是為蒐集證據，惟施虐者已逃離當地，引起不少台灣人關注。<br />\n<br />\n事主在FB「爆廢公社」表示，80歲的爺爺告訴他們被虐待，向中介投訴卻苦無證據，直到他們偷偷用針孔攝錄機偷拍，才發現有人每次向爺爺硬塞一口食物，就會打他一下，甚至起腳踢面羞辱：「沒拍到的地方不知被欺負成什麼樣，80幾歲的老人家被這樣對待，這口氣，誰吞的下？」<br />\n<br />\n事主認為，政府制定法規保護外勞，但也應該制定退場機制：「這種會欺凌病患的外勞，仲介業者也不歡迎這樣的外勞入境台灣。在國外透過面試，外勞都是很誠懇的面容，都說她會努力工作&hellip;&hellip;看看是否能在居留證系統留有紀錄，類似台灣的良民證，這樣仲介在挑選工人（已來過台灣工作者）時，透過居留證查核，就能知道是否有施暴紀錄，惡質的看護不該只是遣送！不該只是遣送！不該只是遣送！此惡劣看護，政府您看見了嗎！」<br />\n<br />\n網民也紛紛留言：「看了好心疼好難過」、「可以不要來台灣賺錢，何必這樣對待老人家，可惡至極」、「應該要留紀錄，讓她不能再來台灣做看護，看到老人家被這樣對待真的很難過」、「為什麼要這樣欺負手無縛雞之力的老人呢？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180902/s00004/1535881874281\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180902%2Fs00004%2F1535881874281&d=hzNM7YY%2BVeW%2BoBM08pddX0zHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=fd62bfca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180902%2Fs00004%2F1535881874281&h=875c3358\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180902/s00004/1535881874281</a>"},{"pid":"98320651b2a7ed145ef30b1c8aa6f6445ca8998d","tid":804407,"uid":54502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T03:57:09.000Z","msg":"香港d廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2acf0460ba0f271d86d957f95bcaf826588626a","tid":804407,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T04:02:12.000Z","msg":"有得奶腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aee40d8de2b93bea489ee091f8d123d4fc896e6","tid":804407,"uid":4811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T04:03:39.000Z","msg":"為咗搵錢要請低等民族做家務，仲要被虐代真係好諷刺，到最後賺錢為何<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"186407d5563683f74e98f391401c2fbfc853c2bc","tid":804407,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T04:18:43.000Z","msg":"腳板好白滑"}]}